name: WhatMemeareYou
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: what meme are you
des: Take this test to see which meme matches up better with your personality. You will be asked three questions and the meme that best matches your responses will be given to you. You can also request information on the meme after it is selected.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
